<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>zhǔ yé sū hǎo mù rén 迦南203</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ yé sū hǎo mù rén, tā wèi wǒ men shě mìng,
 fān shān yuè lǐng bǎ wǒ men zhǎo huí,
 qīng cǎo de xī shuǐ biān ràng wǒ men xiǎng ān xī,
 bù jī è bù gàn kě, yǒng bù huì shī mí.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>203</hymn_number>
</song>